==Notable people==
* Allen Aaron Cook, an architect, was born here in 1832
* Nancy Matthews Elliott was born here in 1810 and became the mother of Thomas Edison.
* Serranus Clinton Hastings, U.S. Congressman and founder of the Hastings College of the Law at University of California

