* Arthur &quot;Bomber&quot; Harris, RAF
* Curtis LeMay, USAF
* Billy Mitchell, USAAS
* Alexander P. de Seversky in &quot;Victory Through Air Power&quot; (1942 book and 1943 film)
* Carl Spaatz, USAF
* Hugh Trenchard, RAF

